# Ignore Dockerfiles (including environment-specific variants)
**/Dockerfile
**/Dockerfile.*
**/dockerfile
**/dockerfile.*

# Ignore Docker Compose files
**/docker-compose.yml
**/docker-compose.yaml
**/docker-compose.*.yml
**/docker-compose.*.yaml

# Ignore dotenv files with sensitive values
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
